## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingsetnodeid">FoldingSetNodeID</a> - This class is used to gather all the unique data bits of a node.

When all the bits are gathered this class is used to produce a hash value for the node.

Definition at line 327 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/foldingset-h">FoldingSet.h</a>.
